{"tid":2509710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［新聞自由］鏗鏘集《記者的出路》接管理層通知不能播出 但表示「沒有原因」","createTime":"2021-04-29T15:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T02:10:26.000Z","uid":243259,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cb09dc180cf8b97c0d66438070426c1e9f824245","tid":2509710,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"香港電台鏗鏘集以《記者的出路》為主題的報道，早前被管理曾延期播出，其製作團隊今日（29 日）正式接獲管理層通知，該集報道不能播出，但表示「沒有原因」。製作團隊表示，在過去一個月內，有積極和管理層溝通，盡力爭取報道出街，無奈未能改變結局。<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3nvGCLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nvGCLA&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=07844829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3nvGCLA</a>"},{"pid":"40697698a4d44658d46e53cbd5ca91dec59adf37","tid":2509710,"uid":243259,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"新聞自由又贏 搵唔到位入<br />\n直接無原因 cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c98cfbfc730247b